thread.title: BRIEF-Holly Energy Partners Announces Delaware Basin Diesel Supply Project

title: BRIEF-Holly Energy Partners Announces Delaware Basin Diesel Supply Project

organizations.name: brief-holly energy partners announces delaware basin diesel supply project

text:
May 1, 2018 / 10:41 AM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Holly Energy Partners Announces Delaware Basin Diesel Supply Project Reuters Staff
May 1 (Reuters) - Holly Energy Partners LP:
* HOLLY ENERGY PARTNERS ANNOUNCES DELAWARE BASIN DIESEL SUPPLY PROJECT
* HOLLY ENERGY PARTNERS LP - PLANS TO CONSTRUCT A TRUCK LOADING RACK IN ORLA, TX
* HOLLY ENERGY PARTNERS LP - COST OF PROJECT IS ESTIMATED BETWEEN $10 MILLION AND $20 MILLION
* HOLLY ENERGY PARTNERS LP - CONSTRUCTION WILL COMMENCE IN Q2 AND IS EXPECTED TO BE COMPLETED IN Q4 OF 2018
* HOLLY ENERGY PARTNERS - EXPECTS TO ENTER LONG-TERM THROUGHPUT AGREEMENT CONTAINING MINIMUM ANNUAL THROUGHPUT COMMITMENTS WITH HOLLYFRONTIER Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
